snippet.title: Warframe | Abyss of Dagath - Official Gameplay Trailer - Coming This Week To All Platforms!
snippet.description:
Celebrate the frightful Nights of Naberus with Warframe’s latest update, Abyss of Dagath!

Meet the terrifying 54th Warframe initially introduced at TennoCon 2023: Dagath. This faceless warrior curses foes with high damage-dealing Abilities. Once you hear Grandmother tell her tragic story you’ll never again underestimate the wrathful power of despair!

Coming to the Origin System alongside Dagath are a host of additional Quality-of-Life improvements: take command of the high seas like never before thanks to Hydroid’s major new rework. Then continue your aquatic journey with an improved Waverider quest as you obtain Yareli. You’ll also enjoy greater vitality for your Companions (goodbye, permadeath!), as well as many other adjustments and changes to streamline your Warframe experience. Plus, everyone’s favorite gluttonous gourmand rolls into battle with the forthcoming introduction of Grendel Prime Access.

►► WHAT IS WARFRAME?

Join 70M+ registered players in Warframe, a cooperative, free-to-play third-person looter shooter set in a constantly evolving sci-fi universe. For more info, visit https://warframe.com. 

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PlayWarframe/ 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlayWarframe 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playwarframe/ 
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/warframe
